            <p class="privacy-heading">
<b>Q:&nbsp;How do I see the homes I'm following or the searches I've saved on the phone? </b> <br/>
<b>A:</b>&nbsp;From any screen in the app, click on My Account in the bottom menu to see homes you're following and saved searches.
<br/><br/>

<b>Q:&nbsp;How do I filter my search? </b><br/>
<b>A:</b> &nbsp;You can filter your results (for example, set a price range, specify the number of bedrooms, etc...) by tapping on the Filter button in the menu at the top of the screen.
<br/><br/>
        
<b>Q:&nbsp;How do I save my favorite searches and properties? </b> <br/>
<b>A:</b>&nbsp;Just tap the Save button at the bottom of the search screen, or the Star button on a Property screen, and your search or property will be saved. We&#39;ll also automatically keep you updated on any changes including new properties in your search area, and any property updates. We&#39;ll also automatically keep you updated on any changes including new properties in your search area, and any property updates.
<br/><br/>
                
<b>Q:&nbsp;How do I save my searches and follow properties? </b> <br/>
<b>A:</b>&nbsp;Following homes or saving searches to your Aqarabia account is easy! Simply tap on the star symbol in the menu at the top of the screen. Note that you need a Aqarabia account to follow homes or save searches, so you may be prompted to login or signup.
<br/><br/>

<b>Q:&nbsp;How do I change the search location? </b> <br/>
<b>A:</b>&nbsp;Change your location by tapping on the filter button at the top of the search results screen and input your location. You can search for a city, country, neighborhood and full property address. If searching for a property address or neighborhood, be sure to include the city and state as well.
<br/><br/>
                
<b>Q:&nbsp;How do I add an Open House entry to my calendar?</b> <br/>
<b>A:</b>&nbsp;You can add the Open House time and place to your phone's calendar by tapping on the Open House time on the property details screen. We automatically add it to your calendar for you!
<br/><br/>

<b>Q:&nbsp;Why can&#39;t I find a property? </b> <br/>
<b>A:</b>&nbsp;Aqarabia for iPhone displays properties from brokers or agents who submit their listing information to Aqarabia. We currently have thousands of listings in our system and are adding new ones every day.
<br/><br/>
                
<b>Q:&nbsp;Why do the properties update when I move the map on the Android App? </b> <br/>
<b>A:</b>&nbsp;When you move the map of search results, the properties update to show you the properties in that map area. You can zoom in and out or tap through the properties to see more or less results.
<br/><br/>
                
<b>Q:&nbsp;How do I contact someone about properties I&#39;m interested in? </b> <br/>
<b>A:</b>&nbsp;You can contact an agent or broker about properties directly from the property page by tapping the Contact button at the bottom of the screen. You can call or email the listing agent directly.
<br/><br/>

<b>Q:&nbsp;How can I give you feedback about the IPhone app? </b> <br/>
<b>A:</b>&nbsp;We love your feedback! Please email IOS (at) Aqarabia dot com, and include the phone model you are using. Thanks!
<br/><br/>

<b>Q:&nbsp;How do I unsubscribe from Aqarabia emails? </b> <br/>
<b>A:</b>&nbsp;Every Aqarabia email contains an &quot;unsubscribe&quot; link at the bottom of the email text - simply click this link to unsubscribe from the email. Or, you can visit the main Aqarabia website and manage all your email alerts in one place.
<br/><br/>

<b>Q:&nbsp;What is the &quot;featured local expert&quot; I see in some searches? </b> <br/>
<b>A:</b>&nbsp;Featured local agents/experts are Aqarabia partners who can help you learn more about real estate when you are ready for a personal touch in your real estate search. Simply click-to-call or email them to begin a personal conversation!
<br/><br/>
Still need help? Email us at <a href="mailto:customersupport@aqarabia.com" style="color: #00ad6a;">customersupport@aqarabia.com</a>
